ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENT:
Any use, modification, or distribution of this Software, whether in source or
binary form, requires prominent attribution to Open Launch in the following manner:

1. If used in a web application, website, or any online service:

   - A visible dofollow link to "https://open-launch.com" must be displayed on ALL pages of your website (preferably in the footer)
   - You MUST use one of the official "Powered by Open-Launch" visual badges:

     Light Theme Badge:
     https://open-launch.com/images/badges/powered-by-light.svg

     Dark Theme Badge:
     https://open-launch.com/images/badges/powered-by-dark.svg

   - For implementation code and examples, visit: https://open-launch.com/legal/badges
   - Text-only attribution is NOT sufficient and will not fulfill the license requirements
   - The badge must be clearly visible to users and not hidden, obfuscated, or made smaller than 150x44 pixels
   - The link must be a dofollow link (do NOT add rel="nofollow" attribute)

2. If used in offline applications or printed materials:

   - Credit must be given in the format: "Powered by Open Launch (https://open-launch.com)"

3. If used in derivative works or modifications:
   - The attribution requirement applies to all derivative works
   - This license must be included with any redistributed software

